    "description": {
      "content": "Recurring CNAB (Brazilian banking text-file) statement extraction for Efí Pay accounts. Schedule daily/weekly CNAB jobs, list generated files, and download them via the API or via SFTP using a generated key pair.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Efí Pay Developer Support",
